===Etymology===

bi + [[week]] + -ly

===Adverb===
'''biweekly''

#Occurring [[once]] every two weeks.
#[[Twice]] every [[week]] without fail.


====Synonyms====
*[[semi-weekly]]
*(2): [[fortnightly]] (''British English'')

====Usage note====
Because of the ambiguity of this word, it is best to avoid it.  Instead, use ''twice a week'', ''every two weeks'' or ''fortnightly'' as appropriate.

Correctly refers to "every 2 weeks."

